  "texts": [
    "The authors evaluated their approach on UTD-MHAD [49] and MSR-Action3D [50], achieving high accuracy.The integration of a CNN-LSTM hybrid model is a prevalent approach in both human activity recognition [26,27,34,[51][52][53], and disease classification [54].",
    "Lakhan et al.",
    "employed a CNN-LSTM architecture in proposing a framework for detecting Autism Spectrum Disorder.",
    "Liao et al., [34] also introduced a deep learning architecture that combines CNN and LSTM networks to evaluate physical rehabilitation exercises.",
    "Their framework proficiently classifies exercises in the UI-PRMD dataset, demonstrating practicality with low absolute deviation per exercise."
